@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Create Arena (מחזיר tournamentId + joinUrl)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/arena
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ArenaX - Blitz",
  "clockTime": 3,
  "clockIncrement": 2,
  "minutes": 30,
  "rated": false
}

### Sync games for latest arena (לא צריך להדביק ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/arena/latest/sync-games?max=50

### Get saved games with moves/winner/colors (לא צריך ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/arena/latest/games
